<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٤٩٩٥ - ابْنُ عُيَيْنَةَ، عَنْ عَمْرٍو،<span class="c5"> عَنْ عُبَيْدِ بْنِ عُمَيْرٍ:</span> <span class="c1">" <span class="c3">{لِكُلِّ أَوَّابٍ حَفِيظٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[ق: ٣٢]</span> "</span>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«الَّذِي لَا يَجْلِسُ مَجْلِسًا ثُمَّ يَقُومُ إلَّا اسْتَغْفَرَ اللَّهَ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>